      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCKY MCQUEEN (8) comes back to 1200m today after some solid form over the 1400m in recent events. His only run over this course and distance was a screamer and the form out of that was strong. Likely to be in the second half of the field but he should be flying late. THE HEIR (2) flew home from the back of the pack to just miss at this track and trip last time out, beaten 0.3L. He now draws inside and being able to take up a closer position could prove the difference. Rates highly off his latest performance and another forward showing is on the cards. LEAN MASTER (11) has been disappointing in recent efforts, but he returns to his preferred track and trip today. The inside draw should see him handy to the speed and he's getting down in the handicap now. Can bounce back in a big way. KING GLORIOSO (4) was super here fresh as a 30-1 chance and that rating stacks up. Can feature in the finish again.",
